summary: I watched Killing Eve at last and my two favourite relationships were (spoilers below the cut)[[MORE]] Eve and Bill in the...
body:
I watched Killing Eve at last and my two favourite relationships were (spoilers below the cut)

Eve and Bill in the early-series and Anna and Villanelle in the late-series. So given the deaths, I’m not sure who I’m excited for in series 2?

I thought I would care about Eve/Villanelle a lot more than I did, but it was never anywhere near as compelling as those other relationships, to me. 

While I’m under here, hands down the best thing, not including every scene was Bill or Carolyn was in, was Anna shouting ‘no!’ when Eve asked if she and Villanelle had had sex… and Villanelle in a later scene talking about the best sex they had. I *l o v e d* it. Good repressed gay content.

summary: I know its early, but any ideas on how you want Eve and Villanelle to get together?
question: I know its early, but any ideas on how you want Eve and Villanelle to get together?
answer:
I’m not sure if I want them together as in, a comitted and exclusive couple, partly because I don’t really know how realistically plausible that is lol. But it mostly depends on what route they take with Eve’s character.

If they do what I think they’re gonna do, and have Eve get progressively darker throughout the course of the show, I could see the two of them becoming a dysfunctional pair of murdering lovers, which is the closest I could currently see them to becoming a “couple”.

But if they have Eve stay mostly on the good side and have her fight back against her draw to the darkness, I could see her and Villanelle continuing to be “enemies” but with a lot of hate sex and the connection and obsession between the two of them still being very present.

I think between those scenarios, i’d prefer the first, but i’d be cool with the second one too. I don’t necessarily need them to be “together” as long as I get some actual pay-off from the gay obsession. Like, if we never see them kiss or fuck, i’ll personally be kind of pissed lol.
